{{TCWRetcon|{{InsiderCite|73|Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 15:01:13}}}}The '''Chancellery Walkway''' was a street in the [[Jrade District/Legends|Jrade District]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was lined with the monuments and memorials constructed in remembrance of the most influential [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellors]]. It was the location of the [[Finis Valorum Memorial]].

